title: [1508521049] Roast Pumpkin Soup (Part 1) - Gordon Ramsay
description:
In the Ramsay household, nothing goes to waste. See how Gordon creates an incredible pumpkin soup with roasted seeds and mushrooms. Perfect for autumn. 

The official YouTube channel of Gordon Ramsay, with exclusive clips from a selection shows including Cookalong Live, Gordon's Great Escape and more. Subscribe for weekly videos. 

To find out more about Gordon Ramsay visit:
www.gordonramsay.com
